{"tid":2330521,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"請台灣政府立即調查華碩叛國行為","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T18:43:26.000Z","uid":48234,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba42bb469c5d7a57287024b92258151b9f874fea","tid":2330521,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be919554cd514b8135a06a58b4eeaee8e7fb74b","tid":2330521,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">捉拿賣國賊<br />\n強制華碩向全球客戶道歉<br />\n還大家一個堅守原則，保護個人私隱的華碩</span></span>"},{"pid":"eda4d2acf3d4cfb67b5f22b97a66dc699d9bb5c3","tid":2330521,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"76134a21bb007adb6e5fb77e0e7acb857c9c9dbb","tid":2330521,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">老鳳擁有的多數電子產品，牌子都是華碩<br />\n包括電腦硬件，手提電話<br />\n亦一向有推薦華碩產品<br />\n今次華碩的行為不但屬於叛國行為<br />\n老鳳亦感到自己被華碩背叛<br />\n非常心痛</span></span>"},{"pid":"4b4315e06aa58021eb14e41aa2f3232b7cc1dc1e","tid":2330521,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5efbcecd7d8f365a69dc09887522c812f7a013d","tid":2330521,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9272235096a8476929202554472f853a4271b8d4","tid":2330521,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4b4315e06aa58021eb14e41aa2f3232b7cc1dc1e","tid":2330521,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T18:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n無恥沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)肯向香港手足道歉未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252543</a><br />\n<br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9272235096a8476929202554472f853a4271b8d4","tid":2330521,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T18:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n無恥沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)肯向香港手足道歉未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252543</a><br />\n<br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\"